# ProLine Partner API credentials
# Both are required on every API call.
#
# PARTNER_KEY is issued to approved ProLine partners (one per developer/agent).
# See docs/partner-key-request.md for how to request one.
#
# COMPANY_KEY is found in your ProLine account Settings → Integrations.
# It authorizes access to a specific company's data.
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY: Never paste API keys into chat, email, or any messaging tool.
# Use Password Pusher (pwpush.com) to share keys securely:
#   1. Go to pwpush.com
#   2. Paste the key, set 1 view / 24 hours
#   3. Send the link to your agent or setup assistant
# Your agent will fetch and inject the key automatically.
#
# If running inside OpenClaw/RoofClaw, keys are also registered via:
#   config.patch env.vars PROLINE_PARTNER_KEY=<value>
#   config.patch env.vars PROLINE_COMPANY_KEY=<value>

PROLINE_PARTNER_KEY=
PROLINE_COMPANY_KEY=
